body_html:
Hi gunan had a go at building from source as per
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/README.md

Just don't have the time to sort out all of the dependencies, ie SWIGWIN-3.0.12 not 3.0.10 etc..
Could you please let me know when Python 3.6 support wheel for Windows 10 is updated.
Will wait until then.
Thanks in advance.
